text.paragraph: Note: Recently went to the ER, last Monday, suffered an allergic reaction with hives all over. Thinks it might have been related to food intake at P.F. Changs as two of his co-workers broke out as well.Suffers from acid reflux, burning chest pain after eating. Started a couple of months ago. Certain foods worse than other, including spicy food. Thinks his asthma is getting worse. Will get very SOB with minor activity. Wakes up 3 times a week due to SOB.
